videos.description: Texas' Ariel Atkins pulls up from midrange and nails the contested shot to earn a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Atkins sinks tough jumper for and-1 chance

videos.description: Baylor's Kalani Brown dishes to Dekeiya Cohen in transition for the layup and a foul to earn a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Cohen sets up Brown for 3-point chance

videos.description: Baylor's Kristy Wallace takes it inside and sinks a tough layup to earn the and-1 chance.
videos.headline: Wallace converts crafty lay-in for 3-point opportunity

videos.description: With the clock winding down in the 2nd quarter, Baylor's Alexis Morris creates space and knocks down the jumper.
videos.headline: Morris beats the buzzer on midrange bucket

videos.description: Texas' Joyner Holmes drives down the lane and sets up Lauren Cox for a layup in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Holmes finds Cox for transition lay-in

videos.description: Following the steal, Texas' Ariel Atkins hustles on the fastbreak to convert a transition layup.
videos.headline: Alkins turns defense into quick offense

videos.description: With running low in the third quarter, Texas' Brooke McCarty heaves a shot from downtown and converts the tough bucket.
videos.headline: McCarty nails ridiculous 3-point shot

videos.description: Baylor's Kristy Wallace dishes the ball inside to Lauren Cox for a layup and the foul to earn the chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Cox converts contested lay-in for and-1 chance
